{"tid":2177911,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"大腸鏡住院問題","createTime":"2020-08-28T04:59:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-03T17:33:10.000Z","uid":31208,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"05319805e6153fa87d7e9bf32d65e58d2c9d246e","tid":2177911,"uid":31208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T04:59:49.000Z","msg":"1)<br />\n之前一晩要痾清，咁如果我同其他人共用一間房得一個廁所咪好麻煩？<br />\n<br />\n定做日間好? 咁之前嗰晚可以喺屋企搞<br />\n<br />\n2）<br />\n唔想做全身麻醉，係咪做監察麻醉訓覺都係可以？"},{"pid":"20877b8c836bfa4ace6fd708157b923130d2344b","tid":2177911,"uid":53660,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"05319805e6153fa87d7e9bf32d65e58d2c9d246e","tid":2177911,"uid":31208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T04:59:49.000Z","msg":"1)<br />\n之前一晩要痾清，咁如果我同其他人共用一間房得一個廁所咪好麻煩？<br />\n<br />\n定做日間好? 咁之前嗰晚可以喺屋企搞<br />\n<br />\n2）<br />\n唔想做全身麻醉，係咪做監察麻醉訓覺都係可以？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T05:12:57.000Z","msg":"1<br />\n一間房有兩個廁所<br />\n<br />\n你會一路痾，忍唔住，梗係去左醫院先<br />\n<br />\n2<br />\n可以，但全身唔係好d咩?"},{"pid":"953da0c1f137cd61a7b0822faa4d9ddf0611c979","tid":2177911,"uid":198841,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T07:36:17.000Z","msg":"1. 緊係係屋企痾好好多啦, 痾乾淨仲可以沖涼<br />\n2. 監察麻醉足夠了, 好似訓教咁, 訓醒已經行得走得"},{"pid":"7a651c74545e9a81cfb34f3dcd34bf428b941aea","tid":2177911,"uid":190660,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T10:29:49.000Z","msg":"上星期照完<br />\n前一晚屋企痾完<br />\n第二朝九點做<br />\n十點幾走得了"},{"pid":"6d3807f5e560339bf3e0b4ec999d0fa705862da3","tid":2177911,"uid":98387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T10:31:46.000Z","msg":"一定屋企"},{"pid":"19594d91427d07d7a75989b8ea45c13ee622136b","tid":2177911,"uid":31962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T10:35:01.000Z","msg":"之前浸會做（公司保險）<br />\n夜晚入去 全晚要飲瀉藥 同屙<br />\n早上做都未屙到好清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我全身麻醉做完都唔知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好難飲Cheers"},{"pid":"1ba1579fa95863ab2bd058f1d5db74ed4d592b41","tid":2177911,"uid":98387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T10:35:04.000Z","msg":"我個次做日間 其實個種麻醉 係令你比人通完櫃都冇感覺<br />\n做完活動正常 仲去食野添<br />\n<br />\n至於痾個度 我建議一定起屋企<br />\n我個次痾到放棄用紙巾(敏)屎<br />\n直接用花灑清潔"},{"pid":"0bc9abf87df99ca48b73ab184533bcfde75117d3","tid":2177911,"uid":48266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T10:42:43.000Z","msg":"1. 睇你住咩房架姐 大房要share屎坑 你有錢住私家房咪自己一個屎坑<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實日間做都得 做完訓陣起身走得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 係"},{"pid":"cc7859d8fe1b6a49ebd8a2b4c1396483d77b647d","tid":2177911,"uid":11716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T10:44:03.000Z","msg":"照個腸鏡唔會用全身麻醉<br />\n通常都係麻醉師監測下麻醉，打粒鹽水豆，打d藥落去<br />\n因為訓左覺，感覺好似全身麻醉咁，但絕對冇插喉駁機幫你透氣"},{"pid":"88362847e4ca4c8e768a718066f1feade5881ea4","tid":2177911,"uid":208422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"19594d91427d07d7a75989b8ea45c13ee622136b","tid":2177911,"uid":31962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T10:35:01.000Z","msg":"之前浸會做（公司保險）<br />\n夜晚入去 全晚要飲瀉藥 同屙<br />\n早上做都未屙到好清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我全身麻醉做完都唔知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好難飲Cheers"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T10:47:47.000Z","msg":"真 訓醒已經係出面等緊"},{"pid":"b6f7338bfcea4aed60ddac01c10c3267f0da6c5e","tid":2177911,"uid":71058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T10:49:30.000Z","msg":"醫生冇話你知點做咩?"},{"pid":"8481ec8ae46a91ed56eeb5de83a1eda78f64ca01","tid":2177911,"uid":38691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc7859d8fe1b6a49ebd8a2b4c1396483d77b647d","tid":2177911,"uid":11716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T10:44:03.000Z","msg":"照個腸鏡唔會用全身麻醉<br />\n通常都係麻醉師監測下麻醉，打粒鹽水豆，打d藥落去<br />\n因為訓左覺，感覺好似全身麻醉咁，但絕對冇插喉駁機幫你透氣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T11:33:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔會有麻醉師 又唔係大手術 只會有兩個護士同一個醫生"},{"pid":"2ab7b9d17f1792f9fd588982113af455eb313397","tid":2177911,"uid":76681,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T12:00:30.000Z","msg":"住過半私家, 2人 share , 好在對方唔是照大腸鏡, 否則<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n馬桶爆炸<br />\n<br />\n飲潟藥, ALL 成晚, <span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">ALL完即灌1L 水, 想嘔都要迫自己飲</span></span>, 因為直接影響腸內清晰度( 你多屎痴住)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n如果醫生用olympus 靚機,有 「窄頻成像（NBI，Narrow Band Imaging）」技術, 會夜視功能咁, 睇得更清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第朝, 醫生同麻醉師陪你, 一打麻醉針, 爽到呢.............問你叫咩名, 2秒就訓撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一醒來( ~1小時), 醫生又出現眼前, 面露笑容, 除了告訴你大腸無事外, 也流露出他對又<span class=\"blue\">開發了新菊花的滿足感</span>。"},{"pid":"06bd3af4a03fb7f4886e8b7fae8c1d5ce3a6918b","tid":2177911,"uid":115179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T15:47:27.000Z","msg":"搵朱大腸驗過腸，好人都算有良心"},{"pid":"df718e58be9e8decdd82620c7caa166f04d7b374","tid":2177911,"uid":279789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T16:04:46.000Z","msg":"痾嘅時候菊花會唔會好似腸胃炎咁好撚痛？"},{"pid":"3e64f7c483d22aa0ccd9af9403001ba1707de757","tid":2177911,"uid":350194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T16:21:37.000Z","msg":"其實上面有照過嘅巴打 係因為自己有明顯嘅病徵先去定點 我除咗多屎屙之外 冇黑便 屙血體重下降 唔知睇唔睇好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34af9c317dc7c67fdaa710aed2e8a6f91f273785","tid":2177911,"uid":198841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e64f7c483d22aa0ccd9af9403001ba1707de757","tid":2177911,"uid":350194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T16:21:37.000Z","msg":"其實上面有照過嘅巴打 係因為自己有明顯嘅病徵先去定點 我除咗多屎屙之外 冇黑便 屙血體重下降 唔知睇唔睇好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T23:33:27.000Z","msg":"你應該係腸胃敏感發炎之類，我係持續腸痛去照，有一粒好細瘜肉順便割左安心哂"},{"pid":"e06fc21593c503ed4f5f128b21014e02304693c8","tid":2177911,"uid":208422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e64f7c483d22aa0ccd9af9403001ba1707de757","tid":2177911,"uid":350194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T16:21:37.000Z","msg":"其實上面有照過嘅巴打 係因為自己有明顯嘅病徵先去定點 我除咗多屎屙之外 冇黑便 屙血體重下降 唔知睇唔睇好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T23:57:56.000Z","msg":"我係照胃鏡..順便照埋腸<br />\n之後發現粒瘜肉..割埋"},{"pid":"7b42d3202076cf103ff579b0b59c559aa11ce05c","tid":2177911,"uid":91979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"34af9c317dc7c67fdaa710aed2e8a6f91f273785","tid":2177911,"uid":198841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e64f7c483d22aa0ccd9af9403001ba1707de757","tid":2177911,"uid":350194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T16:21:37.000Z","msg":"其實上面有照過嘅巴打 係因為自己有明顯嘅病徵先去定點 我除咗多屎屙之外 冇黑便 屙血體重下降 唔知睇唔睇好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T23:33:27.000Z","msg":"你應該係腸胃敏感發炎之類，我係持續腸痛去照，有一粒好細瘜肉順便割左安心哂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T17:33:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}